<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/03/17/iphone-18-pro-c2-modem-rumor/"><strong>Apple's custom-designed C2 modem</strong></a>, with mmWave 5G support in the United States</li><br/>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/22/iphone-18-camera-control-button-simplified/">A redesigned Camera Control button</a></strong>, with a focus on pressure-sensitive controls, rather than swipe gestures</li></ul>Read our <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/iphone-18/">iPhone 18 roundup</a> for more information.<div class="linkback">Related Roundup: <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/iphone-18/">iPhone 18</a></div><div class="linkback">Related Forum: <a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/forums/iphone.99">iPhone</a></div><br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/09/23/iphone-18-pro-early-rumors/">Skipped the iPhone 17 Pro? Here&#039;s What is Rumored for iPhone 18 Pro</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/skipped-the-iphone-17-pro-heres-what-is-rumored-for-iphone-18-pro.2467242/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>